{"tid":2517072,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《自肥企画》「Big壁精奴」遊戲明寸TVB  ERROR二創《新世紀福音戰士》勁好評","createTime":"2021-05-05T05:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T05:41:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b43aca318e196681d3f82024b08f94d3a324052b","tid":2517072,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:41:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210505/DDD6XJFSD5HAZLKRXOZECB3YGQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210505%2FDDD6XJFSD5HAZLKRXOZECB3YGQ%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=afae99eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210505%2FDDD6XJFSD5HAZLKRXOZECB3YGQ%2F&h=454500ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210505/DDD6XJFSD5HAZLKRXOZECB3YGQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n《自肥企画》「Big壁精奴」遊戲明寸TVB <br />\nERROR二創《新世紀福音戰士》勁好評<br />\n<br />\n人氣組合ERROR前晚推出新遊戲節目《ERROR自肥企画》，首集甫開始，四子即cosplay日本經典動畫《新世紀福音戰士》幾位主角出場，重演動畫的首集劇情，甚至二創片頭曲改為節目主題曲，除了鏡頭、畫面勁似外，惡搞歌詞抵死搞笑；他們首個遊戲「Big壁精奴」更是以諧音明寸無綫的「big big channel」，加上「肥仔」梁業講香港現況的貼地對白，獲網民洗版留言狂讚。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：四度炸「生啤」越炸越旺<br />\n<br />\n組合ERROR主持的ViuTV新節目《ERROR自肥企画》前晚首播，近日四子人氣急升，不少觀眾都非常期待新節目。節目甫開始先由四子和「Double S」沈殷怡及陳欣妍重演經典卡通《新世紀福音戰士》首集劇情，何啟華（阿Dee）扮「碇真嗣」、梁業（肥仔）扮「碇司令」、郭嘉駿（193）扮「綾波麗」及吳保錡扮「EVA初號機」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OsCwYte1pl2rPmGcDz7Wxu_w6ww=/802x697/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VN5BEBSH6JFVHNZEQTHMP7RCKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOsCwYte1pl2rPmGcDz7Wxu_w6ww%3D%2F802x697%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVN5BEBSH6JFVHNZEQTHMP7RCKQ.jpg&h=5b42a4b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■ERROR四子以精蟲look玩「Big壁精奴」遊戲，擺明寸無綫的big big channel。電視圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RE1N6nedPc3GpCPBKCoNRWJPzKI=/802x1168/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T62H5LEBBNCH7JW6OC4LX354GI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRE1N6nedPc3GpCPBKCoNRWJPzKI%3D%2F802x1168%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT62H5LEBBNCH7JW6OC4LX354GI.gif&h=1d7aabb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■ERROR四子在前晚播出的《ERROR自肥企画》cosplay動畫《新世紀福音戰士》的人物，不論造型、鏡頭，都似足原著。電視圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_QcI92YA3THAwHU7ILfBzDob-Ng=/802x359/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/URZPG3WVWZGF3HQZXS2T7V4PBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_QcI92YA3THAwHU7ILfBzDob-Ng%3D%2F802x359%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FURZPG3WVWZGF3HQZXS2T7V4PBA.jpg&h=7c008030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳欣妍（左二）與沈殷怡在節目分別扮演葛城美里及赤木律子。電視圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMike導主唱夠啜核<br />\n<br />\n「碇司令」肥仔在節目中指，香港面對「經濟、疫情、精神健康，全部冧檔」、「唔移民嘅話，香港呢個爛攤子，點都係你㗎，面前嘅困境，有冇能力打敗佢」等危機，因而要啟動ERROR作戰狀態，早前「反省中」的保錡以機械人造型出場時自嘲：「終極即係冷卻狀態，即係被雪藏。」網民大讚重演劇情時，連鏡頭方向都跟足原著動畫，是誠意十足，加上影射香港現況的對白，令人看得很有感覺。<br />\n<br />\n接着再播出改編自《新》片頭曲《殘酷天使的行動綱領》、由旁白麥可暉填詞及格仔導演劉諾衡（Mike）主唱的主題曲，歌詞「係咁OT我畀埋條命你好冇」、「妥協後到最後諗真我係要玩彈XX打爆隻蛋」、「面對收視的壓力是但啦頂你個肺」等幾乎全部錯key兼三級，不過依然被大讚「貼地、啜核」，道出不少港人及電視人的心聲。其後四子以全白精蟲look大玩「Big壁精奴」遊戲，發音刻意跟無綫的「big big channel」相近，擺明寸無綫。遊戲中四子要一齊撞牆，當中會有三人跌入油漆中，順利過關的一人贏得1,000元獎金，最後由阿Dee勝出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qBvlycRnZTtXz51OUFKor3pG69o=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KQC3PYXU7BBFVGZG4QMRXYOLBQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqBvlycRnZTtXz51OUFKor3pG69o%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKQC3PYXU7BBFVGZG4QMRXYOLBQ.jpg&h=b2fa01c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■節目主題曲無厘頭加入舊有的泳裝鏡頭，令人發笑。電視圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/I758V3QJeCX_VA6krEEN-UaZLL0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3V2DFTPT45GKXIKPKKKFD4BSKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FI758V3QJeCX_VA6krEEN-UaZLL0%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3V2DFTPT45GKXIKPKKKFD4BSKM.jpg&h=cd26a140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■主題曲的歌詞夠貼地、啜核，獲得網民一致激讚。電視圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張敬軒：年度最愛<br />\n<br />\n節目播出後，網民即迅速瘋狂式洗版留言大讚：「全港最強團隊，ViuTV要加人工！」、「叫對面台所謂嘅創意總監收X啦」，不少網民更特別力讚搞鬼主題曲，連張敬軒也在保錡於Ig貼出的幕後花絮帖文中留言「我聽咗首歌10次！」更形容是年度最愛。對於新節目首集大獲好評，193昨日回覆《蘋果》時表示：「真係要多謝網民咁留意我哋，拍嗰陣已經好好笑，之後我自己偷睇咗頭三集，估唔到剪完出嚟仲好笑。其實我哋係現今藝能界最多cosplay嘅藝人，希望遲啲可以去到啲動漫展。」<br />\n<br />\n今次《ERROR自肥企画》繼續由跟四子合作無間的格仔導演Mike、編導「Agent L」曹梓沖及「無制限OT編集團」幕後團隊炮製，對於網民熱捧，Mike前晚也在Ig限時動態留言感謝大家支持，並透露正全力進行其他集數的後期工作：「現在猛烈地追趕剪接進度中，絕對一定冇辦法覆得晒大家，你哋嘅支持同鼓勵係收到嘅，多謝你哋呀，每一位觀眾！」不過，日前Mike卻爆粗炮轟ViuTV的公關，指他們上周向傳媒發出新聞稿，劇透首集炸吉祥物「生啤」等情節，力斥公關的逆向宣傳破壞他們幕後一番心血及浪費事前的保密功夫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/X9Y_Ep41mN72bskfUtYpeAsPQJE=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NPQ3QKYGAFFNFL345HSKUGRFS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FX9Y_Ep41mN72bskfUtYpeAsPQJE%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNPQ3QKYGAFFNFL345HSKUGRFS4.jpg&h=ba781651&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■數度被炸的生啤榮升「生啤神」，更被團隊惡搞配音變麻甩仔。電視圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/07WjMuqgMseDtQWK5sc2IoAartM=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CSFQEDBYJFCO7FGSBN53M4EDKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F07WjMuqgMseDtQWK5sc2IoAartM%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCSFQEDBYJFCO7FGSBN53M4EDKU.jpg&h=6bffa90e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■今次炸生啤時，節目組加入字幕「脫離壓逼，自由萬歲」，網民也讚有心。電視圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QnSMMpwt0anzAdeo--O8qZjYfkc=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SVRUIEX5QNAZLI5CS4PETOA4GI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQnSMMpwt0anzAdeo--O8qZjYfkc%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSVRUIEX5QNAZLI5CS4PETOA4GI.jpg&h=97d4d094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Mike導（左三）炸完生啤後帶着Agent L（左一）等幕後現身，被讚有型。電視圖片"}]}